Overrun by tourists and dirty
Mar 2018 ‚Ä¢ Couples
People are offered either a day trip or a 2 day/ 1 night trip on the boat to see Halong Bay.
We did the second option and we went to a beach and did a small hike on the first day and went to see a cave in the second day. Both places were awfully touristy, too crowded, toilets super dirty and discusting and everywhere plastic swimming in the ocean.
Facit:
My advice - don't bother to visit Halong Bay, it's dirty and overrun by tourist boats that spoil the natural environment! It's very sad hopefully the government will take some action here soon.
